#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:875
msgid ""
"This unit has immunity to slows, poison, fire damage, cold damage, and "
"arcane damage."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:900
msgid "Fort Garard"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:915
msgid "The ruins of Fort Garard. This is where my father died."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/overworld/00e_eastern_wesnoth.cfg:919
msgid ""
"Yes. You know the story. The darkest hour of my darkest day; a crime born of "
"my haste and my arrogance. Had I been but a breath wiser that night, all "
"might have been different..."
msgstr ""

