msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:909
msgid ""
"That guard was carrying some kind of strange device! Whatever it was, we "
"slew him with such a mighty blow that he had not the chance to use it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:914
msgid ""
"Well done! We slew this guard with such a mighty blow that he had not a "
"chance to destroy his bridge."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:933
msgid "The fire is getting to the explosive powder! Your Majesty—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:942
msgid "Argh! Your Majesty... it doesn’t even need to walk..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:947
msgid "Argh! Your Majesty... the plan..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:952
msgid "Carry out your orders. Do not disappoint me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1029
msgid "So. After burning half my fields, these rebels come at last to face me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1034
msgid "So, these rebels come at last to face me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lisar {LISAR_VARIATION mad}
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1039
msgid ""
"Surrender, mother. The land’s blood is spent. I have come to take my "
"rightful place."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1043
msgid ""
"Ahh. My own daughter, a turncoat. Such treason my reign must endure! But "
"endure it will."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1047
msgid ""
"For the walls of Weldyn are strong. And her allies are many! They will "
"arrive in days — and then you will die."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1067
msgid ""
"Knights from the Horse Clans, footmen from Dan’Tonk, and orcish hordes from "
"the north now swollen even further with your mage Mirya’s new recruits. We "
"know, and we are prepared."
msgstr ""

