#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Heir_To_The_Throne/scenarios/50_The_Battle_for_Wesnoth.cfg:1075
msgid ""
"Footmen from Dan’Tonk and orcish hordes from the north. We know, and we are "
"prepared."
