"war, they are unorthodox but brilliant strategists who can direct even the "
"freshest recruits to strike strategically against imposing odds and emerge "
"victorious. Outfitted in finely-made weapons and armor, these leaders are a "
"force to be reckoned with in both warfare and single combat."
